## Chart Conventions

### Choose the right chart type

| Data type | Chart |
|---|---|
| Trend over time | Line chart |
| Part-to-whole | Donut (max 5 segments) or stacked bar |
| Comparison | Grouped bar |
| Distribution | Histogram or box plot |
| Relationship | Scatter |

**Never use pie charts** — donut only, max 5 segments, labeled outside.

### Chart defaults

```tsx
// Recharts defaults — apply to every chart
const CHART_DEFAULTS = {
    margin: { top: 4, right: 16, bottom: 4, left: 4 },
    animationDuration: 300,
}

// Axis labels: always small, muted
<XAxis
    tick={{ fontSize: 12, fill: '#9CA3AF' }}
    axisLine={false}
    tickLine={false}
/>

// Tooltip: simple, no borders
<Tooltip
    contentStyle={{ border: 'none', boxShadow: '0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.08)', borderRadius: 8 }}
    labelStyle={{ fontWeight: 500 }}
/>
```

### Color palette for charts (use in order)

```ts
export const CHART_COLORS = [
    '#3B82F6',  // blue-500 — primary series
    '#8B5CF6',  // violet-500
    '#10B981',  // emerald-500
    '#F59E0B',  // amber-500
    '#EF4444',  // red-500
]
// Never use more than 5 series in one chart — split into two charts instead
```

